agent_selection_prompt:
Analyze this architecture decision and recommend 4 specialist review agents.

Subject: {subject}

Context: {context}

Each agent must score these dimensions: scalability, maintainability, security, performance.

Respond ONLY with a JSON array of agent definitions:
[
  {
    "agent_name": "Specific Name",
    "role": "Area of Expertise",
    "focus": "What this agent evaluates",
    "evaluation_criteria": ["criterion 1", "criterion 2", "criterion 3"]
  }
]
